Foreseend changes for geant4 incorporation into AMS

-------
Platform:
linux-g++ and dec-cxx >= v6.1

-------
Installer:


source install/g4i

<recommended>
setenv AMSWD smth
mkdir $AMSWD/bin
mkdir $AMSWD/exe

gmake -if install/Moptg4
n.b
setenv AMSDEBUG 1 switch on debug mode
unsetenv AMSDEBUG switch it off

